---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Tithe.ly giving">
  <h1>Tithe.ly giving</h1>

  <p>External-link integration for online giving via Tithe.ly. v1 ships an embedded link only; webhook integration for member-side giving history is on the v1.x roadmap.</p>
  <h2>Setup</h2>
  <p>Site Settings → Branding → set the giving URL to your Tithe.ly church page. The "Give" link in the public nav redirects there.</p>
</BaseLayout>
